to install:

	npm install
	brew tap homebrew/science
	brew install clustal-omega
	pip install -U pip
	pip install seqmagick


pipeline:

	cat data/emydura-short.gb | ./bin/genbank-fasta.js - | ./bin/clustal-o.js - | ./bin/fasta-to-nexus.js - | ./bin/mrbayes.js - | ./bin/consensus-newick.js -

if you are using a fasta file from genbank, substitute `./bin/sanitize-fasta.js -` for the genbank-fasta script.

to convert files:

	seqmagick convert --input-format fasta --output-format nexus --alphabet dna <input> <output>
